<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Área do Paciente</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 600px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #2d3e50;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .strong {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2d3e50;
    }

    a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #fff;
      background-color: #2d3e50;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    a:hover {
      background-color: #1c2a37;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Bem-vindo(a), <%= paciente.nome %>!</h1>
    <p>Seu tipo de convênio: <span class="strong"><%= paciente.tipo_convenio %></span></p>
    <p>Para agendar consultas, entre em contato por telefone conforme instruções do convênio.</p>
    <a href="/logout">Sair</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
